videos.headline: Troy WR reaches out and scores TD
videos.description: Troy wide receiver Deondre Douglas catches the pass and reaches for the goal line, scoring the 6-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: South Alabama WR makes the catch and dives for the TD
videos.description: South Alabama wide receiver Jordan McCray grabs the pass from Evan Orth and reaches to the end zone for the 16-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Troy RB explodes up the middle for rushing TD
videos.description: Troy running back B.J. Smith takes the hand off and speeds his way through the hole and into the end zone for the 36-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Troy QB uses play-action fake for TD throw
videos.description: Troy quarterback Sawyer Smith fakes the hand off and then finds Damion Willis for the three-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: South Alabama QB takes it on TD strike
videos.description: South Alabama quarterback Evan Orth takes a hit and is still able to get throw off, finding Jamarius Way for the 31-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Troy QB powers way into end zone
videos.description: Troy quarterback Sawyer Smith gets the snap and shows off the strength scoring a 1-yard TD.
